summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1909, for the improvement of West 57th Street in the City of Seattle, from 9th Avenue Northwest to 26th Avenue Northwest; by regrading, curbing and constructing concrete sidewalks, with all necessary appurtenances; under Ordinance No. 19656 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
